data.description:
SELLER will pay up to $5000 in buyer closing costs 
'The Winterset'' one of the largest Keystone home plans available.  This well cared for home is like new (built in 2021) and definitely has a very generous amount of space for everyone!  Enter into a dynamic 2 story foyer with large double door closet.  Open concept Living room, Dining room and Kitchen great for entertaining.  Kitchen features a large corner walk in pantry and island with extra seating.  Granite counter tops and stainless steel appliances (top of the line Samsung refrigerator like new condition to remain with acceptable offer)
Dining area with sliding glass door opens to freshly painted patio area.  Large fenced yard with permanently built in fire pit.  The main level has a Master Suite with walk in shower, soaking tub, private toilet area, large linen closet, as well as an impressive walk in closet, and granite vanity with double sinks. On the main level as well is a beautiful powder room, large storage closet and an area at garage entry big enough for extra storage and seating (lots of possibilities for this space).  Garage has easy to clean chalk paint on 2 walls and kid safe cushioned snap together flooring area.
Upstairs opens to a large Den / loft area with storage closet, large laundry room, 2 full baths, and 4 generously sized bedrooms all with ceiling fans and walk in closets.  Additional features include: Easy to maintain luxury vinyl flooring, Carpeted areas that have been professional cleaned and sanitized, Double water heaters, sprinkler system for front and backyard. Front landscaping beds have fresh mulch with new resin boarder and fresh pine straw has been added to several areas of the yard as well.
